#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/lowpower.rst:2
#: 199e16592b0e496c828d12bada0c9e84
msgid "低功耗"
msgstr "Low Power"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/lowpower.rst:17
#: b0e64c6685264127ab4f9b4bd52e1fe0
msgid "进入低功耗模式后电流异常是什么原因？"
msgstr "What causes abnormal current after entering low-power mode?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/lowpower.rst:18
#: 4edb21e680c34a94866f87df62bdbada
msgid ""
"当正常进入PDS时电流一般100uA~200uA，正常进入HBN时电流一般<5uA， 如果电流在几"
"百uA则说明有power domain未关，如果电流超过10mA则一般是程序跑飞所导致的。"
msgstr ""
"When the device enters PDS normally, the current is generally 100μA-200μA. "
"When the device enters HBN normally, the current is generally <5μA. If the "
"current is several hundred μA, it indicates that some power domain has not "
"been turned off. If the current exceeds 10mA, it is generally caused by the "
"program running abnormally."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/lowpower.rst:23
#: ad2b2385d24c46f586e971290d5d12c0
msgid "电流未能如期降低，为什么直接升高到mA级别？"
msgstr ""
"Why does the current fail to decrease as expected and instead rise directly "
"to the mA level?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/lowpower.rst:24
#: 1050495d309e4845b10c9dd6d5e90937
msgid ""
"当发现电流未能降低至uA级别就直接上升到10mA以上时，一般是程序跑飞导致， 出现此"
"问题优先考虑是否在PDS_Mode_Enter中关闭flash之后又访问了flash的地址"
"0x23xxxxxx，可以通过反汇编对此进行确认，PDS_Mode_Enter内关flash与开flash之间"
"绝不应该出现0x23xxxxxx地址。如果是此问题导致，则优先确认链接脚本中是否没把"
"ATTR_CLOCK_SECTION、ATTR_CLOCK_CONST_SECTION、ATTR_TCM_SECTION、"
"ATTR_TCM_CONST_SECTION、ATTR_DTCM_SECTION等放到TCM区域，其次确认此过程中是否"
"有变量在flash上。 还有可能是代码中所使用到的某些API没使用这些链接属性修饰。"
msgstr ""
"When the current fails to drop to the μA level and instead rises directly "
"above 10mA, it is generally caused by the program running abnormally. When "
"this issue occurs, first check whether the Flash address 0x23xxxxxx is "
"accessed after Flash is disabled in PDS_Mode_Enter. This can be confirmed by "
"disassembly. There should absolutely be no 0x23xxxxxx address between "
"disabling Flash and enabling Flash in PDS_Mode_Enter. If this is the cause, "
"first check whether ATTR_CLOCK_SECTION, ATTR_CLOCK_CONST_SECTION, "
"ATTR_TCM_SECTION, ATTR_TCM_CONST_SECTION, ATTR_DTCM_SECTION, etc. are not "
"placed in the TCM area in the linker script. Then check whether any "
"variables are located in Flash during this process. Another possibility is "
"that some APIs used in the code are not modified with these link attributes."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/lowpower.rst:29
#: dac61099fa5b4bb0997e01e36c212bea
msgid "能正常进入低功耗，但无法正常唤醒，如何解决？"
msgstr ""
"The device can enter low-power mode normally but cannot wake up properly. "
"How can this be solved?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/lowpower.rst:30
#: 57ce25df588f428a8a9e762cfd46c5ee
msgid ""
"需要确认所需中断是否正常配置（低功耗中断需要配置，相应外设中断也需要配置），"
"查找问题时可以考虑使用PDS/HBN自身的timer唤醒来做对比验证， 确认是没正确配置唤"
"醒源还是确实PDS/HBN模式配置错误，然后继续查找原因。"
msgstr ""
"You need to confirm whether the required interrupts are configured "
"correctly. Low-power interrupts need to be configured, and the corresponding "
"peripheral interrupts also need to be configured. When troubleshooting, you "
"can consider using the PDS/HBN timer wake-up function itself for comparison "
"and verification. Confirm whether the wake-up source is not configured "
"correctly or whether the PDS/HBN mode configuration is indeed incorrect, and "
"then continue investigating the cause."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/lowpower.rst:34
#: 95f9b3421d2b450384b02d6f8007108a
msgid "为什么在IOT_SDK运行异常，在MCU_SDK运行正常？"
msgstr "Why does it run abnormally in IOT_SDK but normally in MCU_SDK?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/lowpower.rst:35
#: 9d50b68bc46e44fdb6d8edf59ac8aadd
msgid ""
"MCU_SDK平台相对简单，一般不会出现进出PDS/HBN异常的情况。IOT_SDK平台较为复"
"杂， 不过一般是因为其所使用的stddriver没有更新到最新版本所导致，因此IOT_SDK跑"
"低功耗的case时需要优先更新stddriver到最新。"
msgstr ""
"The MCU_SDK platform is relatively simple, and generally there will not be "
"abnormal cases when entering or exiting PDS/HBN. The IOT_SDK platform is "
"more complex. However, this is generally caused by the stddriver used by "
"IOT_SDK not being updated to the latest version. Therefore, when running low-"
"power cases in IOT_SDK, you should first update stddriver to the latest "
"version."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/lowpower.rst:40
#: b01fd3cc6d4d4e14b59685381d91d84f
msgid "低功耗模式下电流比预期大了几十uA，如何解决？"
msgstr ""
"The current in low-power mode is dozens of μA higher than expected. How can "
"this be solved?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/lowpower.rst:41
#: 17bc323ec40346e1b0da039fe5fe4eec
msgid ""
"flash pad floating会导致漏电（50uA~100+uA）。faraday memory进行读写后无法正常"
"进入retension模式会导致电流偏大（20uA左右）。 进入低功耗后某些GPIO没有HighZ会"
"导致电流增大。为了从低功耗模式唤醒所打开的外设会导致电流偏大（如HBN模式使用"
"acomp唤醒）。"
msgstr ""
"Flash pad floating may cause leakage current (50μA-100+μA). If faraday "
"memory cannot correctly enter retention mode after read/write operations, "
"the current may become larger (about 20μA). After entering low-power mode, "
"some GPIOs not being set to HighZ may increase the current. Peripherals "
"enabled for wake-up from low-power mode may also increase the current, such "
"as using acomp wake-up in HBN mode."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/lowpower.rst:46
#: cdcc193754a84aeabc92eda04514cac7
msgid "注意事项"
msgstr "Notes"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/lowpower.rst:47
#: cbcea610e0b84e6584b923bec5db8466
msgid ""
"1.进入PDS前若关闭了flash，则需要保证关flash后的代码都不在flash上，否则跑飞。"
msgstr ""
"If Flash is disabled before entering PDS, make sure that all code executed "
"after Flash is disabled is not located in Flash; otherwise, the program will "
"run abnormally."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/lowpower.rst:49
#: 98c6cef9a3b5413a838b83e61b79bb5e
msgid "2.若需要使用JLINK调试，则JLINK所用的GPIO不能被HighZ。"
msgstr ""
"If JLINK debugging is required, the GPIOs used by JLINK must not be set to "
"HighZ."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/lowpower.rst:51
#: eb40dbc917bb44f288165306722b95b8
msgid ""
"3.602使用的是faraday的memory，其特性为程序在将TCM/OCRAM设置为retension模式后"
"如果又对TCM/OCRAM区域进行了写操作，则会导致这些区域自行退出retension模式，继"
"而使得电流稍大（20uA级别）。"
msgstr ""
"602 uses faraday memory. Its characteristic is that after the program sets "
"TCM/OCRAM to retention mode, if a write operation is performed on the TCM/"
"OCRAM area again, these areas will automatically exit retention mode, "
"causing the current to become slightly higher (around 20μA)."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/lowpower.rst:53
#: e48b9427e1384e21ac52a5f29783e2ab
msgid ""
"4.sram有idle、retension、sleep三种模式，正常读写sram时其处于idle模式，idle模"
"式电流较大，retension模式下不能对sram进行读写但此时进入低功耗后数据可以保留，"
"retension模式电流较小，sleep模式下sram掉电所有数据全部丢失，sleep模式电流最"
"小。"
msgstr ""
"SRAM has three modes: idle, retention, and sleep. During normal read/write "
"access to SRAM, it is in idle mode, which consumes relatively high current. "
"In retention mode, SRAM cannot be read or written, but data can be retained "
"after entering low-power mode, and the current is relatively low. In sleep "
"mode, SRAM is powered down and all data is lost; sleep mode has the lowest "
"current consumption."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/lowpower.rst:55
#: ca950772cb5b435fb1852706e0742f61
msgid ""
"5.PDS模式需要37个clock（32K）的时间来warm up，因此存在最小睡眠时间的限制37，"
"软件结构体中的睡眠时间必须超过此数值。"
msgstr ""
"PDS mode requires 37 clocks (32K) to warm up, so there is a minimum sleep "
"time limit of 37. The sleep time in the software structure must exceed this "
"value."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/lowpower.rst:57
#: f8313fbaa3154eda96da3eed17af157a
msgid ""
"6.当使用PDS的qon pad唤醒时，需要注意，由于ro_pds_irq_in中断会同时受到多个irq"
"的影响而置一，因此在清此标志位之前，需要确保其所包含的多个irq都已经被clear"
"掉，否则即使设置了cr_pds_int_clr，也会由于“hbn_irq_out | (gpio_irq) | "
"irrx_int | ble_slp_irq | reg_en_platform_wakeup & platform_wake_up”而使得"
"ro_pds_irq_in再次被置一（尤其是HBN内GPIO7/8的IRQ标志位），因此需要在设置aon "
"pad唤醒PDS时，先清一下这些标志位。"
msgstr ""
"When using the PDS qon pad wake-up function, note that the ro_pds_irq_in "
"interrupt can be set by multiple IRQs at the same time. Therefore, before "
"clearing this flag bit, you must ensure that all IRQs included in it have "
"been cleared. Otherwise, even if cr_pds_int_clr is set, ro_pds_irq_in will "
"be set again due to “hbn_irq_out | (gpio_irq) | irrx_int | ble_slp_irq | "
"reg_en_platform_wakeup & platform_wake_up” (especially the IRQ flags of "
"GPIO7/8 in HBN). Therefore, when setting aon pad wake-up for PDS, clear "
"these flag bits first."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/lowpower.rst:59
#: 85c29b46b1e14136881e4dc0287d7441
msgid ""
"7.只要唤醒源在(hbn_wakeup)，就没办法hbn sleep。所以当唤醒源标志位未清时，"
"0x4000F000[7]置一并不会进入hbn，程序会继续向下运行。"
msgstr ""
"As long as the wake-up source is in (hbn_wakeup), HBN sleep cannot be "
"entered. Therefore, when the wake-up source flag bit is not cleared, setting "
"0x4000F000[7] will not enter HBN, and the program will continue running."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/lowpower.rst:61
#: 4f1987eb6d4b4b0d82faa4ef35935afe
msgid ""
"8.为了避免因flash pad floating而导致的漏电，需要正确设置相应pad的pull，建议全"
"部上拉。"
msgstr ""
"To avoid leakage caused by Flash pad floating, correctly configure the pull "
"state of the corresponding pads. It is recommended to pull all of them up."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/lowpower.rst:63
#: eb6f3a2e51814237adb7557aa4b50a2b
msgid ""
"9.在进入PDS/HBN之前需要确保相应低功耗模式下有效的唤醒源中断全都被清除过，否则"
"有可能无法正常进入PDS/HBN。"
msgstr ""
"Before entering PDS/HBN, make sure that all wake-up source interrupts valid "
"in the corresponding low-power mode have been cleared. Otherwise, the device "
"may fail to enter PDS/HBN properly."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/lowpower.rst:65
#: fed4a7728a3345419aadae376e87f5f8
msgid ""
"10.在测试PDS/HBN时遇到异常现象时，建议优先接上电流表，可以方便排查问题。"
msgstr ""
"When abnormal phenomena occur during PDS/HBN testing, it is recommended to "
"first connect an ammeter, which can help troubleshoot the problem."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/lowpower.rst:69
#: e8352b6646cf47ed88c34bea7de35250
msgid "请问WB2-12F模组进入深睡模式之后，能否收到WiFi消息？"
msgstr ""
"Can the WB2-12F module receive Wi-Fi messages after entering deep sleep mode?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/lowpower.rst:70
#: 7640b58be9514bdb9b4fdea74c9b7a53
msgid "WB2系列模组进入深睡之后均无法收到WiFi消息；"
msgstr ""
"After entering deep sleep, WB2 series modules cannot receive Wi-Fi messages."
